                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The blustering gale bashes, batters, and pummels each adjacent enemy (@Check[type:reflex|dc:27|basic:true] save). The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[(1d8+2)[bludgeoning]] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(2d8+12)[bludgeoning]] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(3d8+15)[bludgeoning]] damage</p>"
